If you want the segment to play repeatedly, enable the
"Repeat" button.

When playing a segment, you may use the REW/FF or the
keypad window's track warp slider to move around
within the segment.  If you move to a location before
the start of the segment, playback will start at the
start of the segment.  If you move to a location
after the end point, playback will stop.  Using the
previous/next track, previous/next index, or the
keypad to change tracks in Segment play mode will
cancel the Segment Play mode.

Changing discs (using the eject button, the
previous/next disc button, or using the keypad in
disc mode) will cancel the Segment Play mode.
